OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1777990267
OL,3,CCardiff University fined nearly #300k
OL,4,Cafter employees develop asthma
OL,6,FCardiff University has been fined
OL,7,F#280,000 by the Health and Safety
OL,8,FExecutive (HSE) after it found that
OL,9,Ftwo employees developed occupational
OL,10,Fasthma because of exposure to animal
OL,11,Fallergens in the workplace.
OL,13,FThe HSE found that between 2008 and
OL,14,F2025 the university failed to identify
OL,15,Fand implement suitable controls to
OL,16,Fprevent employees' exposure to animal
OL,17,Fallergens.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
