OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1777990267
OL,3,CCardiff University fined nearly #300k
OL,4,Cafter employees develop asthma
OL,6,FBoth employees are now permanently
OL,7,Fdisabled as a result of the condition,
OL,8,Fwith one unable to continue in their
OL,9,Fjob.
OL,11,FThe university was fined #280,000 and
OL,12,Fordered to pay #11,745 in costs at
OL,13,FCardiff Magistrates' Court on 30 April.
OL,15,FIn a statement one of the affected
OL,16,Femployees discussed the impact on
OL,17,Ftheir life: "I was diagnosed with
OL,18,Foccupational asthma and occupational
OL,19,Frhinitis, and my lung function has
OL,20,Fbeen permanently decreased by 33
OL,21,Fpercent," they said.
OL,26,@yD@MOU
