PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1777990267
OL,3,CCardiff University fined nearly #300k
OL,4,Cafter employees develop asthma
OL,6,F"As a result, my breathing has been
OL,7,Fterrible, and I struggle walking any
OL,8,Fdistance. Going upstairs is really
OL,9,Fdifficult. I have to take steroid
OL,10,Finhaler, a nasal spray and a
OL,11,Fbronchodilator throughout the day as I
OL,12,Fneed it.
OL,14,F"I become breathless when having long
OL,15,Fconversations and I am unable to walk
OL,16,Fand talk at the same time anymore."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@cO]
