OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1777990267
OL,3,CCardiff University fined nearly #300k
OL,4,Cafter employees develop asthma
OL,6,FOccupational asthma is a work-related
OL,7,Ftype of asthma which is caused by
OL,8,Finhaling fumes, gases, dust, or other
OL,9,Fharmful substances at work. It can
OL,10,Fhave serious and permanent
OL,11,Fconsequences.
OL,13,FA HSE spokesperson said: "This was a
OL,14,Fcase of Cardiff University completely
OL,15,Ffailing to identify the risk to
OL,16,Femployees working with animals and not
OL,17,Fputting suitable controls in place to
OL,18,Fprevent exposure.
OL,20,F"The fact this went on unchecked for
OL,21,F15 years is truly concerning.
OL,26,@uD@ZOU|D@AOU
