OL,3,CCardiff University fined nearly #300k
OL,4,Cafter employees develop asthma
OL,6,F"Occupational asthma is a recognised
OL,7,Fwork-related disease with potentially
OL,8,Fdisabling consequences.
OL,10,F"HSE will not hesitate to take action
OL,11,Fagainst organisations, which do not do
OL,12,Fall that they can to keep people safe."
